    <abstract id="aspace_d11db2f873dda47a1d5fabf5621838b3">The collection consists of correspondence, biographies, and ephemera pertaining to the life, career, and memory of Ernest Bloch.</abstract>
    <langmaterial id="aspace_9ccbebbbf5c3298852fbb1835e4bb871">The collection is in <language langcode="eng">English</language>, <language langcode="fre">French</language>, and some <language langcode="ita">Italian</language>. The majority of the Ernest Bloch correspondence is in <language langcode="fre">French</language>French.</langmaterial>
