  <scopecontent id="aspace_53b27a4e94f684c0cda5d881c3c46b8e">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>The collection consists primarily of the correspondence of Ernest Bloch from 1918-1952 (bulk 1918-1928), as well as various biographies, reviews, and lists of Ernest Bloch's work. The collection also contains other materials about memorials and tributes to Ernest Bloch including the Ernest Bloch Society.</p>  </scopecontent>
